                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-phase">
                    <div class="phase-time">2-24 Hours</div>
                    <h3 class="phase-title">Inflammatory Cascade</h3>
                    <p>Neutrophil recruitment, pro-inflammatory mediators amplify response, tissue swelling begins.</p>
